<DocsPageLead>
    Images are a binary representation of visual data.
</DocsPageLead>

<DocsPageParagraph>
    An <Code Tag>Image</Code> component is a visual representation of something, while a digital image is a binary representation of visual data. For this purpose, an image is a picture that was created or copied and stored in electronic form. 
</DocsPageParagraph>

